# Seabright City (biome: city)
# Symbols resolve via assets/tiles.yaml for the "city" biome; the map viewer
# shows the authoritative, data-driven legend with previews. Tiles used here:
# . = cobblestone   % = wall   A-F = houses   M/P/S/R = shops   G = gate
# O = fountain      + = start
# @ = NPC placeholder (bound by >[npc:...] at line end)
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%AABBBCC....GGGGG.....DDDEEE..%
%A....C.......@.........D...E.%  >[npc:city_exit]
%.............................%
%.MMM....PPP.......SSS...RRR..%
%..@......@.........@.....@...%  >[npc:city_weapon_shop], [npc:city_potion_shop], [npc:city_spell_shop], [npc:city_mastery_trainer]
%.............................%
%.AB..CD...............EF..AB.%
%.AB..CD....C.....D....EF..AB.%
%.AB..CD...............EF..AB.%
%.............................%
%..............O..............%
%.............................%
%.EF..AB...............CD..EF.%
%.EF..AB....E.....F....CD..EF.%
%.EF..AB...............CD..EF.%
%.EF..AB...............CD..EF.%
%.............................%
%.............................%
%............................@%  >[npc:culverts_entrance]
%.............................%
%.............+@..............%  >[npc:city_exit]
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
